@NODE bugs "Erk!"

    Firstly, some bug-like features which are actually forced upon me:

        1: Samples must be in IFF 8SVX format
        2: Samples must be no more than 128k long

    There have been initial reports of the Listview not updating.  If you
get this, let @{"me" link author} know and ignore it for now.  Save your
config and reload the prefs program, and the Listview will update.

    If you find any bugs, in either program, the let @{"me" link author} know.
@ENDNODE

