@NODE author "About me"

    WBWelcome was written by Alex Furmanski, a prolific programmer who
seems to spend most of his time glued to his computer chair (a nasty
accident - don't ask).  At the age of 16 (years), he is taking A-Levels in
Computing, Electronics, Maths and Chemistry.  Hands full, then.
    He has been programming for several years, since he started on his ZX
Spectrum in the (very) early nineties.  Over this period, he has knocked up
a few small programs and a couple of major ones which were published on an
AFCD, just like these.  You probably know the name from the excellent Civ
Hack, the latest version of which is also on this CD.

    Should you wish to contact him, write to:

